- [ ] Loading skeleton shown during initial fetch
- [ ] Skeleton matches shape of real cards
- [ ] Error state shown when API fails
- [ ] Error message displayed
- [ ] Retry button triggers refetch
- [ ] Refetch doesn't show loading state (keeps stale data)
- [ ] Proper state hierarchy: loading â†’ error â†’ empty â†’ data

